StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.name: [GetLegalO.enseForType]
StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.body:
(@LegalO.enseTypeID int) AS
SELECT lo.LegalO.enseId, lo.Descrip.on, lot.LegalO.enseTypeId AS TypeId, lot.Descrip.on AS TypeDescrip.on FROM [usmc].[LegalO.ense] lo WITH (NOLOCK) INNER JOIN [usmc].[LegalO.enseType] lot ON lo.LegalO.enseTypeId = @LegalO.enseTypeID AND lo.LegalO.enseTypeId = lot.LegalO.enseTypeId
